strings.Value: {n}Enneo stands with his eyes half-closed, as if resting — or listening to something inaudible.{/n} "It's strange. I had no doubt that today it would be my turn to visit {g|Pharasma}Pharasma's{/g} court — not the chosen one of the most disgusting of the deities. It seems the term of my service is not over yet. Which means there are yet more monsters which will soon kiss their un-life goodbye."
"You helped cure a terrible plague. Accept the gratitude of {g|Pharasma}Pharasma's{/g} faithful servant — and this reward."
